data.eml:eml: Two new species of Chromadoridae (Chromadorida: Nematoda) from the East China Sea

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Huang, Yong, Gao, Qun (2016): Two new species of Chromadoridae (Chromadorida: Nematoda) from the East China Sea. Zootaxa 4144 (1): 89-100, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4144.1.4
